{"questionId":"5945","questionHtml":"<p>A weight <em>W </em>is tied to a trolley of mass <em>M </em>by a light string passing over a frictionless pulley.&nbsp;The trolley has an acceleration <em>a </em>on a frictionless table. The acceleration due to gravity is <em>g</em>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://ib-questionbank-attachments.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/tinymce_asset/asset/4721/Schermafbeelding_2018-08-12_om_09.18.54.png\" alt=\"M18/4/PHYSI/SPM/ENG/TZ2/08\"></p>\n<p>What is <em>W </em>?</p>\n<p>A. &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{Mag}}{{(g - a)}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>M</mi>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mi>g</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n      <mi>g</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>B. &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{Mag}}{{(g + a)}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>M</mi>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mi>g</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n      <mi>g</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>C. &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{Ma}}{{(g - a)}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>M</mi>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n      <mi>g</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>D. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{Ma}}{{(g + a)}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>M</mi>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n      <mi>g</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mi>a</mi>\n      <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>A</p>","meta":{"questionId":"5945","referenceCode":"18M.1.SL.TZ2.8","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"A weight W is tied to a trolley of mass M by a light string passing over a frictionless pulley. The trolley has an acceleration a on a frictionless table. The acceleration due to g","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"8","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Core","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics","2.2 – Forces","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}